# Sphinx autosummary side-effects (see .claude/context/lessons-learned.md)
docs/qiskit_metal.*.rst

# Elmer FEM simulation outputs (from running tutorial notebooks)
*.msh
**/simdata/

# JupyterLite build artifacts (docs/conf.py adds jupyterlite_sphinx)
docs/.jupyterlite.doit.db
docs/_build/

# Tutorial-notebook output artifacts. These are regenerated whenever a
# tutorial is executed; tracking them just makes ``git status`` noisy
# after each run and bloats the working tree of new clones. (Untracked
# from main in chore/cleanup-tracked-junk; the existing ``*.gds`` /
# ``*.msh`` patterns above already prevent re-staging.)
**/shot.png
**/shot750.png
**/my_design*.png
**/batch_output/
**/sweep_output/
